cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.NA, cs.SY, cs.MM 

The paper deals with a deep neural network-based methodology for nonlinear electromagnetic inverse scattering, which involves image processing and signal processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). However, the paper also involves numerical analysis, optimization, and system identification, which are related to cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), and cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper involves experimental validation, which is related to cs.MM (Multimedia).
